thread.title_full: Test Me DNA reviewed by Stephen

author: Stephen
title: Stephen
text: Got the maybe baby tested with the DIY kit, even though the baby was trying to eat the swab (which the kit discouraged), it couldn't be helped, but the results were not harmed in any way. The baby turned out to be mine, would have been nice if the price was cheaper ($175), but it was cheaper than other testing sites/centers.
